<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241232>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Dorsal view of holotype (ZSI 25924, adult female) of Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. Photo by Ishan Agarwal & Varad Giri. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241232/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241233>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Head of Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. holotype, ZSI 25924. A) Dorsal view, B) Lateral view, C) Ventral view. Photo by Ishan Agarwal & Varad Giri. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241233/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241234>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Details of dorsal pholidosis of holotype (ZSI 25924) of Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. showing irregularly arranged longitudinal rows of enlarged, rounded tubercles at midbody. Photo by Ishan Agarwal & Varad Giri. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241234/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241236>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. A) Ventral view of right manus of Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. holotype, ZSI 25924, B) Ventral view of right pes Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. holotype, ZSI 25924. Photo by Ishan Agarwal & Varad Giri. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241236/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241237>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Photo in life of the Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. (specimen not collected). Note the colouration. Photo by B. H. C. K. Murthy." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241237/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241240>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Maximum likelihood phylogeny of South Asian Hemidactylus (Bauer et al. 2010) showing the position of Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. (bold) within the Hemidactylus flaviviridis clade. Other clades are collapsed, numbers at nodes represent support values (posterior probability / bootstrap)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241240/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241238>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. The known distribution of Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. in Chhattisgarh (state boundary highlighted in bold), India: 1, Charama; 2, Near Saranpal (Type locality); 3, Saranpal; 4, Malanjkhudum waterfall; 5, Kondagaon; 6, Jagadalpur." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241238/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241239>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Type locality of holotype of Hemidactylus yajurvedi sp. nov. near Saranpal village, 5 km East of Kanker city, District Kanker, Chhattisgarh, India. Photo by B. H. C. K. Murthy." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241239/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

